{"tid":730262,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"STU48 成員被笑似AV女優,受委屈落淚","createTime":"2018-07-05T09:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T09:54:41.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"53f573f8676ec614450449010051e873d9ce2b9e","tid":730262,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:08:41.000Z","msg":"日本人氣女團「AKB48」的姐妹團「STU48」，去年3月正式出道，團員以日本西部瀨戶內海郵輪上的劇場做為表演舞台，但近日成員之一的森香穗，卻驚爆自己遭經紀人性騷擾，對方說她皮膚白皙，「看起來很像AV女優」，森香穗自覺受到羞辱，淚眼婆娑在直播中泣訴，模樣令人心疼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/nownews2017/nownews_production/images/5b39d7243088d324182cf843_201807021541.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fnownews2017%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5b39d7243088d324182cf843_201807021541.jpg&h=45189571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲森香穗遭經紀人譏笑長得像AV女優。（圖／翻攝Baidu , 2018.07.02）<br />\n<br />\n22歲的森香穗長相甜美可愛，但相較其他團員膚色偏黑，天生白嫩的她卻因此遭到經紀人山本學言語挖苦，森香穗近日在直播中轉述經紀人對她說的話，對方表示：「STU48是樸素的團體，其他團員的膚色都很健康，但妳皮膚太白，看起來很豔，好像AV女優。」森香穗聽了受到打擊，她在直播影片中吐苦水，還哭到雙肩顫抖，頻頻用手拭淚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/storage.googleapis.com/nownews2017/nownews_production/images/5b39d8b20ce59b241e9bf3a2_201807021548.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fnownews2017%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5b39d8b20ce59b241e9bf3a2_201807021548.jpg&h=e24234df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲森香穗在直播中哭得一把鼻涕一把眼淚。（圖／翻攝Ranyar YOUTUBE , 2018.07.02）<br />\n<br />\n粉絲獲悉後痛斥經紀人山本學，並要他立刻離職負責，山本學隨後也在官網發表道歉聲明，解釋是森香穗誤解他的話，澄清自己絕無騷擾意思，也對森香穗及其粉絲表達歉意，表示會深刻反省，但仍然無法平息粉絲的怒火。"},{"pid":"384469c2ccf5ccfe62a387d405f0a5a265b0cf67","tid":730262,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1923d80d0dc7f37baa95affbbcae02b3a70c71","tid":730262,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"日本人好尊重av女優"},{"pid":"e8dc60a76ceede8e098d227d32c2fcbc6515fd5c","tid":730262,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1923d80d0dc7f37baa95affbbcae02b3a70c71","tid":730262,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"日本人好尊重av女優"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:14:23.000Z","msg":"女優好光榮㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c02e4c2f4a615326a398a33adcc16f4ff984e04","tid":730262,"uid":38049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:15:28.000Z","msg":"一年後 AV 出道"},{"pid":"cbac407a0ca564348b92427f36fc0148f72193ae","tid":730262,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1923d80d0dc7f37baa95affbbcae02b3a70c71","tid":730262,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"日本人好尊重av女優"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:51:45.000Z","msg":"老師 ..."},{"pid":"3ea454c810fbbb9d610598f5d8e9eb714bd6884c","tid":730262,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"正啦<br />\n咁就跑出"}]}